OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMost of the day will be dry
OL,6,Fwith variable amounts of cloud and a
OL,7,Ffew light showers. Thickening cloud
OL,8,Fwill bring some rain and drizzle to
OL,9,FShetland later. Fresh west or
OL,10,Fsouthwesterly winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FThis evening will be cloudy
OL,13,Fwith occasional rain or drizzle. Then
OL,14,Fbecoming clearer in the early hours
OL,15,Fwith a few light passing showers.
OL,16,FFresh southwesterly winds.
OL,17,
OL,18,CFriday:FMostly cloudy with the chance
OL,19,Fof a few light showers. Rain will
OL,20,Fspread eastwards during the evening.
OL,21,FFresh southwesterly winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
