OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FEarly
OL,6,Frain on Saturday clearing to sunny
OL,7,Fspells and a few showers. Breezy on
OL,8,FSunday and Monday with a chance of
OL,9,Fshowers, these mainly across Shetland.
